---
title: Honey Halloumi, Bacon & Creamy Avo Salad with Jammy Eggs & Toasted Almonds
description: Don’t worry, this is nothing like your garden variety salad - this one has flavour popping like fireworks. Salty and squeaky
halloumi & bacon next to a soft boiled egg, all wrapped up in crunchy cos lettuce sure sounds like an exciting take on a salad - but we’ll let you try it for yourself.
